		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Fatboy wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">What about GBDK, is that just for programming in C. Know if it's any good? Thanks</div>
<br />
<br />GBDK has never been updated since 2008, but there is Z88DK for C programs, If there is no GB/C Setup for Z88DK, you may build one for it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
