	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Honestly, I doubt any compiler is able to generate efficient enough code for anything beyond simple demos. The GBZ80 is a pretty lousy processor (much less powerful than a real Z80), and its design isn't exactly amenable to C's abstractions.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


